RULES
- Only set target_caller_id when the input explicitly names a roster member by name.
- For BOTH, suggested_slug refers to the Workspace side (e.g., accounts/acme-corp).
- If confidence < 0.7, still produce a best-effort classification.
- Do NOT hallucinate entities not present in the text.
- Reply with ONLY the JSON object. No prose, no markdown fences.
